        dc:description           "Figure 9. Nipponosega yamanei Kurzenko & Lelej ♂ A Head in frontal view B ditto, lateral view C ditto, dorsal view D forewing, pterostigma and R 1 E mesosoma. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 2. General habitus of Amiseginae A Nipponosega yamanei Kurzenko & Lelej, holotype ♀ B ditto, ♂ C Okinawasega eguchii Terayama ♀ D ditto, holotype ♂. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." , "Figure 1. General habitus of Amiseginae A Baeosega humida Krombein, holotype ♀ B B. torrida Krombein, holotype ♀ C ditto, allotype ♂ D Nipponosega lineata sp. nov., holotype ♀. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." , "Figure 8. Nipponosega yamanei Kurzenko & Lelej ♀ A holotype of N. yamanei, head in frontal view B ditto, dorsal view C female from Aichi, gena (arrow indicates occipital carina) D holotype of N. kantoensis Nagase, head in dorsal view E holotype of N. yamanei, mesosoma. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
